## Data Dictionary for `combined_analysis_df`

Below is a data dictionary describing each column in the `combined_analysis_df`:

| Column Name                   | Data Type     | Description                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |
| :---------------------------- | :------------ | :---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| `order_id`                    | `object`      | Unique identifier for each order.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |
| `customer_id`                 | `object`      | Unique identifier for each customer.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |
| `order_purchase_timestamp`    | `datetime64[ns]` | Timestamp of when the order was purchased.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |
| `order_approved_at`           | `datetime64[ns]` | Timestamp of when the payment for the order was approved. If missing, it's imputed with `order_purchase_timestamp`.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |
| `customer_zip_code_prefix`    | `object`      | First five digits of the customer's zip code, indicating location.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |
| `customer_city`               | `object`      | City of the customer.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |
| `customer_state`              | `object`      | State of the customer.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |
| `product_id`                  | `object`      | Unique identifier for each product.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |
| `seller_id`                   | `object`      | Unique identifier for each seller.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |
| `price`                       | `float64`     | The price of the product item.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |
| `shipping_charges`            | `float64`     | The shipping cost for the product item.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |
| `product_category_name`       | `object`      | The name of the product category. Missing values are filled with 'Unknown'.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |
| `product_weight_g`            | `float64`     | Weight of the product in grams. Missing values are imputed with the median.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |
| `product_length_cm`           | `float64`     | Length of the product in centimeters. Missing values are imputed with the median.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |
| `product_height_cm`           | `float64`     | Height of the product in centimeters. Missing values are imputed with the median.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |
| `product_width_cm`            | `float64`     | Width of the product in centimeters. Missing values are imputed with the median.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |
| `order_status`                | `object`      | The current status of the order (e.g., delivered, cancelled, pending). Missing values are filled with 'pending'.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |
| `order_delivered_timestamp`   | `datetime64[ns]` | Timestamp of when the order was actually delivered. Remains `NaT` if not delivered.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |
| `order_estimated_delivery_date` | `datetime64[ns]` | The estimated date of delivery for the order. Remains `NaT` if not applicable (e.g., for non-delivered orders).                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |
| `delivery_lead_time`          | `float64`     | The number of days between `order_purchase_timestamp` and `order_delivered_timestamp`. `NaT` for non-delivered orders.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |
| `delivery_delay`              | `float64`     | The difference in days between `order_delivered_timestamp` and `order_estimated_delivery_date`. Positive values indicate delays. `NaT` for non-delivered orders.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |
| `on_time_delivery`            | `object`      | Categorical variable indicating if an order was 'Delayed', 'On-time/Early', or 'Not Delivered/Pending' based on `delivery_delay`.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |
| `total_revenue`               | `float64`     | The total revenue for an order item, calculated as `price` + `shipping_charges`.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |
| `order_purchase_month`        | `Period[M]`   | The month and year of the order purchase, extracted from `order_purchase_timestamp`.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |
| `revenue_growth_rate`         | `float64`     | The percentage change in total revenue from the previous month, calculated from `monthly_sales`.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |
